doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="utf-8")
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no")
        meta(
            name="description"
            content="Integrum Systems offers system integration, technical consulting, and applied R&D services for research teams, advanced operators, and early-stage technical organizations."
        )
        meta(name="author" content="Integrum Systems")

        title Services — Integrum Systems

        // Favicon
        link(rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/favicon.ico")

        include includes/css.pug

    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100
        main.flex-shrink-0
            // Navigation
            include includes/navbar.pug

            // Page header
            header.bg-fog.py-5.border-bottom
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-8.text-center
                            h1.display-6.fw-bolder.mb-3 Engineering engagement, at depth.
                            p.lead.mb-0
                                | We work with research institutions, advanced builders, and early technical organizations to design, build, and document systems that hold up over time.

            // Services
            section.py-5
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.gx-4.gy-4
                        // Service 1
                        .col-lg-4
                            .card.h-100.p-4
                                .feature-icon.mb-3
                                    i.bi.bi-diagram-3
                                h2.h5.fw-bolder.mb-2 System Integration &amp; Architecture
                                p.mb-3
                                    | We design and implement integration architectures for complex multi-component systems. Emphasis on stable interfaces, explicit data contracts, and documented integration points — built for maintainability from day one.
                                p.font-mono.small.mb-0(style="color: #3b4a5e")
                                    | Scope: end-to-end system design spanning hardware, firmware, and software; interface definition and validation, embedded communication stacks (CAN, Ethernet, serial), sensor and actuator coordination, reliability engineering, and cyber-physical systems integration.

                        // Service 2
                        .col-lg-4
                            .card.h-100.p-4
                                .feature-icon.mb-3
                                    i.bi.bi-terminal
                                h2.h5.fw-bolder.mb-2 Technical Consulting
                                p.mb-3
                                    | Early-stage architecture review, engineering process guidance, and technical decision support. Practical, direct, and documentation-backed. We work with teams making foundational choices about systems they will live with for years.
                                p.font-mono.small.mb-0(style="color: #3b4a5e")
                                    | Scope: fractional CTO and technical leadership, architecture and design reviews, firmware and embedded software audits, technical due diligence, risk and requirements analysis, development process optimization.

                        // Service 3
                        .col-lg-4
                            .card.h-100.p-4
                                .feature-icon.mb-3
                                    i.bi.bi-cpu
                                h2.h5.fw-bolder.mb-2 Research &amp; Development
                                p.mb-3
                                    | We take on applied research and early-stage development work — from feasibility studies and proof-of-concept builds to algorithm development and instrumentation design. Our goal is to bridge the gap between exploratory work and production-ready engineered systems.
                                p.font-mono.small.mb-0(style="color: #3b4a5e")
                                    | Scope: feasibility studies and proof-of-concept builds, controls and automation algorithm development, scientific instrumentation, open-source hardware and tooling, and transitioning research into engineered artifacts.

            // Approach block
            section.py-5.bg-fog
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-7
                            h2.fw-bolder.mb-3 What to expect.
                            p.mb-3
                                | Every engagement begins with a short, paid discovery and scoping phase (1–2 weeks) — written constraints, defined interfaces, explicit risk documentation, and agreement on success criteria before any implementation work starts. We do not scope creep silently; changes are flagged and documented as they arise. Work then proceeds as fixed-scope milestones for defined deliverables, or as a monthly retainer for ongoing technical leadership and execution.
                            p.mb-0
                                | We deliver working systems with documentation that enables you to maintain, modify, and understand what was built — without ongoing dependency on us.

            // CTA strip
            section.py-5.bg-primary
                .container.text-center.py-3(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    h2.fw-bolder.text-white.mb-2 Have a systems problem?
                    p.text-white.mb-4(style="opacity: 0.9")
                        | We engage early and at depth. Bring us a constraint, an architecture question, or an underdefined problem — that is where we do our best work.
                    a.btn.btn-light.btn-lg.px-4(href="contact.html") Contact Integrum

        // Footer
        include includes/footer.pug

        include includes/scripts.pug
